Program: Outlook
Title: Anglo-Indians
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbr5t
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
A look at the identity of and attitiudes towards Anglo-Indians with writer Laura Raychaudhury. Also, a visit to Bolivia's Inti Wara Yassi Wildlife Refuge to hear some of the animals' rescue stories. And, pharmaceutical branding, should it make you remember a product or tell you what it contains?